NAME
    FBP::Demo - FBP::Perl Demonstration Application

DESCRIPTION
    FBP::Demo is a Perl distribution which represents the target output of
    the code generation functionality in FBP::Perl.

    It has been completed (or at least initially aims to be) generated from
    a wxFormBuilder project file, and represents approximately what your own
    own generated distribution should look like when you use a front end
    such as Padre::Plugin::FormBuilder to generate a Perl distributions.

SUPPORT
    Bugs should be reported via the CPAN bug tracker at

    <http://rt.cpan.org/NoAuth/ReportBug.html?Queue=FBP-Demo>

    For other issues, contact the author.

